By Jessica Roy, 
Jared Fogle 's victims are getting some justice. 
According to TMZ , the former Subway spokesperson paid out a million dollars to 10 people who were minors when Fogle either secretly photographed them or paid to rape them. Each victim got $100,000 as part of his plea deal . Four additional victims will also be receiving a payout. 
In addition, Fogle will register as a sex offender, get treatment for sexual disorders, and will serve at least five years in prison.
